achige Popliteraturen vor und beleuchtet Themen wie Gender Bias, Postheroismus und den westdeutschen Blick über die wiedervereinigte Nation hinweg.  afunded by Rosa-Luxemburg-Stiftung  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aCultural Studies. 4aDeutschland. 4aGender Studies. 4aGermanistik. 4aLiteratur. 4aLiteraturwissenschaft. 4aMedien. 4aPopkultur. 4aTempo. 4aZeitgeist. 4aZeitgeistjournalismus. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / German.2bisacsh  aCultural Studies.  aGender Studies.  aGerman Literature.  aGermany.  aLiterary Studies.  aLiterature.  aMedia.  aPopular Culture.  aTempo.  aZeitgeist Journalism.  aZeitgeist.2 aRosa-Luxemburg-Stiftungefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2z978311069629508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2020z9783110704532oZDB-23-DKU40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839451298zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839451298423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839451298/original  a978-3-11-069629-5  DG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2b2020  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2020  aZDB-23-DKUb2020